metadata.name: Tiger Kids Club #1
metadata.description: More than 3.2 million years ago in a metaverse forest, there was a magical sprout that hatched into 4444 of these unique creatures. Later these creatures became known as a special breed of rare “Little Tigers”.After the tigers were born, they left their magical metaverse forest, and migrated far and wide. They became the magical best friends of children all over the world.
